addPermissions

void addPermissions(Permission[] permissions)
Adds permissions from specified array to the entry. Safe to call even if a specified permission already set previously. Specifying any empty permission array does not touch remnove existing permissions.

Parameters:
permissions - permission array, must not be null.

isOwner

boolean isOwner()
Check if this entry has the owner permission to the ACL. An owner of the ACL is the entry that can modify the ACL.

Returns:
true if this entry is an owner, false otherwise.
